{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01W2xZ42sVn4QGqQXVP917qj","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→#!/bin/bash\n     2→# ============================================================\n     3→# CC Web Manager — EC2 一键启动脚本\n     4→# \n     5→# 用法：\n     6→#   1. SSH 到你的 EC2\n     7→#   2. 把整个 cc-web-manager 文件夹上传到 EC2\n     8→#   3. 运行: bash setup.sh\n     9→#   4. 脚本会安装依赖、初始化项目，然后启动 Claude Code\n    10→#   5. Claude Code 会根据 CLAUDE.md 自动开发整个系统\n    11→# ============================================================\n    12→\n    13→set -e\n    14→\n    15→echo \"=========================================\"\n    16→echo \"  CC Web Manager — 环境准备\"\n    17→echo \"=========================================\"\n    18→\n    19→# --- 1. 系统依赖 ---\n    20→echo \"\"\n    21→echo \"📦 安装系统依赖...\"\n    22→sudo apt update\n    23→sudo apt install -y python3 python3-pip python3-venv git\n    24→\n    25→# --- 2. 检查 Node.js ---\n    26→if ! command -v node &> /dev/null; then\n    27→    echo \"📦 安装 Node.js...\"\n    28→    curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_22.x | sudo -E bash -\n    29→    sudo apt install -y nodejs\n    30→fi\n    31→echo \"✅ Node.js $(node --version)\"\n    32→\n    33→# --- 3. 检查 Claude Code ---\n    34→if ! command -v claude &> /dev/null; then\n    35→    echo \"📦 安装 Claude Code...\"\n    36→    npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n    37→    echo \"\"\n    38→    echo \"⚠️  请先运行 'claude /login' 登录你的 Claude 账号\"\n    39→    echo \"   登录完成后重新运行本脚本\"\n    40→    exit 1\n    41→fi\n    42→echo \"✅ Claude Code 已安装\"\n    43→\n    44→# --- 4. Python 依赖 ---\n    45→echo \"\"\n    46→echo \"📦 安装 Python 依赖...\"\n    47→cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\"\n    48→pip install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages 2>/dev/null || pip install -r requirements.txt\n    49→\n    50→# --- 5. 创建必要目录 ---\n    51→echo \"\"\n    52→echo \"📁 创建目录...\"\n    53→mkdir -p data logs backups static\n    54→\n    55→# --- 6. 初始化 Git ---\n    56→if [ ! -d \".git\" ]; then\n    57→    echo \"📁 初始化 Git 仓库...\"\n    58→    git init\n    59→    git add -A\n    60→    git commit -m \"Initial commit: project skeleton with CLAUDE.md\"\n    61→fi\n    62→\n    63→# --- 7. 初始化目标项目目录 ---\n    64→PROJECT_DIR=\"${CC_PROJECT_DIR:-$HOME/my-project}\"\n    65→if [ ! -d \"$PROJECT_DIR\" ]; then\n    66→    echo \"📁 创建目标项目目录: $PROJECT_DIR\"\n    67→    mkdir -p \"$PROJECT_DIR\"\n    68→    cd \"$PROJECT_DIR\"\n    69→    git init\n    70→    echo \"# My Project\" > README.md\n    71→    git add -A\n    72→    git commit -m \"Initial commit\"\n    73→    cd -\n    74→fi\n    75→\n    76→echo \"\"\n    77→echo \"=========================================\"\n    78→echo \"  ✅ 环境准备完成！\"\n    79→echo \"=========================================\"\n    80→echo \"\"\n    81→echo \"接下来有两种方式启动开发：\"\n    82→echo \"\"\n    83→echo \"方式 A: 让 Claude Code 自动开发整个系统（推荐）\"\n    84→echo \"  cd $(pwd)\"\n    85→echo \"  claude --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    86→echo \"  然后输入: 请阅读 CLAUDE.md，按照里面的架构设计，开发完整的 CC Web Manager 系统。先从 MVP 开始：实现任务提交、单实例执行、实时日志展示。\"\n    87→echo \"\"\n    88→echo \"方式 B: 让 Claude Code 非交互式地一步步开发\"\n    89→echo \"  claude -p '请阅读 CLAUDE.md，先实现 database.py（数据库初始化和CRUD操作）' --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    90→echo \"  claude -p '请阅读 CLAUDE.md，实现 config.py 的完善和 dispatcher.py（任务调度器）' --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    91→echo \"  claude -p '请阅读 CLAUDE.md，实现 server.py（FastAPI 后端，包含所有 API 和 WebSocket）' --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    92→echo \"  claude -p '请阅读 CLAUDE.md，实现 static/index.html（单文件 PWA 前端）' --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    93→echo \"  claude -p '请阅读 CLAUDE.md，实现 worktree_manager.py 并测试整个系统能否启动' --dangerously-skip-permissions\"\n    94→echo \"\"\n    95→echo \"=========================================\"\n    96→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ce4yJiBd8ysyTXH3pea5HJ","session_id":"4ed89809-b941-4f90-90c8-d74444d0dc9e","uuid":"18071e31-1dcb-45fd-8986-c76f8c50411f"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01PzS3XBJEnWfTxjsYeA9EJB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0135eEiEFsMvvrbR4e1P1iCX","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/cc-web-manager/PROMPTS.md"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14971,"cache_read_input_tokens":36400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":14971},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ce4yJiBd8ysyTXH3pea5HJ","session_id":"4ed89809-b941-4f90-90c8-d74444d0dc9e","uuid":"4478ada9-df38-4a6e-9487-2576a15a2f5b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0135eEiEFsMvvrbR4e1P1iCX","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Claude Code Prompt 速查表\n     2→\n     3→> 这些是你在手机上常用的 prompt 模板。可以直接复制粘贴，也可以语音输入后微调。\n     4→\n     5→## 🔧 功能开发类\n     6→\n     7→```\n     8→开发一个 [功能名称] 功能。要求：\n     9→1. [具体要求1]\n    10→2. [具体要求2]\n    11→确保有错误处理，完成后 commit。\n    12→```\n    13→\n    14→```\n    15→在 [文件路径] 中添加 [具体功能]，保持现有代码结构不变。\n    16→```\n    17→\n    18→```\n    19→参考 [某个文件或模块] 的实现方式，开发一个类似的 [新功能]。\n    20→```\n    21→\n    22→## 🐛 Bug 修复类\n    23→\n    24→```\n    25→[页面/功能] 出现了 [问题描述]。请排查原因并修复。\n    26→修复后在 PROGRESS.md 中记录这个 bug 的原因和解法。\n    27→```\n    28→\n    29→```\n    30→运行 [命令]，如果报错请修复。反复测试直到通过。\n    31→```\n    32→\n    33→## 🎨 UI 优化类\n    34→\n    35→```\n    36→优化手机端的 [页面/组件] 显示效果：\n    37→- 字体太小，增大到适合手机阅读的大小\n    38→- 按钮间距太近，增加间距\n    39→- 加载时显示 loading 状态\n    40→```\n    41→\n    42→## 📝 代码质量类\n    43→\n    44→```\n    45→Review 当前代码，找出潜在的 bug 和可优化的地方。\n    46→修复问题后更新 PROGRESS.md。\n    47→```\n    48→\n    49→```\n    50→给 [模块] 添加错误处理和日志记录。\n    51→确保所有 subprocess 调用都有 timeout 和异常处理。\n    52→```\n    53→\n    54→## 🚀 系统运维类\n    55→\n    56→```\n    57→检查系统运行状态，确保：\n    58→1. 数据库连接正常\n    59→2. 所有 API 端点可访问\n    60→3. WebSocket 连接正常\n    61→4. 自动备份在正常运行\n    62→如有问题请修复。\n    63→```\n    64→\n    65→```\n    66→优化系统性能：\n    67→- 检查是否有内存泄漏\n    68→- 优化数据库查询\n    69→- 清理过期日志文件\n    70→```\n    71→\n    72→## 💡 小技巧\n    73→\n    74→1. **任务描述要具体**：不要说\"优化一下\"，要说\"把任务列表的加载速度优化到 1 秒以内\"\n    75→2. **一次一个任务**：不要把多个不相关的需求塞到一个 prompt 里\n    76→3. **提供上下文**：如果涉及特定文件，在 prompt 中提及文件路径\n    77→4. **让它自测**：在 prompt 末尾加上\"完成后自行测试，确保功能正常\"\n    78→5. **沉淀经验**：重要任务完成后加一句\"更新 PROGRESS.md\"\n    79→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ce4yJiBd8ysyTXH3pea5HJ","session_id":"4ed89809-b941-4f90-90c8-d74444d0dc9e","uuid":"7dbf1dde-0f8c-41fb-ac0e-b51fbe885853"}
